Text: Not the best electro house album out there but not too bad. Theres quite a few old songs on it (whether u think thats a good thing or a bad thing). This torrent has the front and back cover and 3 non-stop Mp3's. You'll have to go out and find the cue sheets if you want to split the MP3's :)
